          "description": "<p>项目背景：针对多站实验室自动化等复杂场景<br><br>技术栈：Vue 3 + TypeScript + Webpack + Element Plus</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": "019cdac9-ced9-7259-99db-bdf86690da3d",
          "hidden": false,
          "options": {
            "showLinkInTitle": false
          },
          "name": "Skylab",
          "period": "2021-12 ~ 2022-12",
          "website": {
            "url": "",
